NOLLYWOOD actor and filmmaker, Alesh Ola Sanni has disclosed the first step he takes after shooting x rated scenes. The US-based actor and entrepreneur told The Nation that due to the nature of his job and family life, he makes sure he sends the behind-the-scenes clips to his wife immediately after shooting. Sanni said this is important because he wouldn’t want anything to cause a misunderstanding between himself and his wife so he has made it a routine.   Drums roll for Coal City film festival     AGN partners StarTimes for content production     Laolu Gbenjo set for one of kind US Tour   “If I should do any nudity movie, I used to have the behind the scenes so once I’m done with it I always send it to her right away because this movie can come out anytime and you will see it. Nobody is perfect but we must use our common sense”, said Alesh. He continues: “If someone wants to be in a relationship with a public figure, you should be able to accept a lot of things that you will be seeing because you know not everything are real on social media, they will say so many things about you with so much scandal, and so are you ready for all those things? - Advertisement - “One thing I always tell my wife is that do not believe whatever you see on social media until I confirm it to you. Trust is love and everything but if we don’t trust each other, forget about it”. SPONSORED